  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Talk to passengers, but wisely! Choices made in the dialogue system influence the plot and the ending especially. Beware - some words thrown may throw you off the train.<br></li><li> Can't open a door? Look at your inventory, and try to drag and drop things from it on a scene.<br></li><li> Explore level - point over things in the car, maybe some of them can be picked up, and some other objects are of different use.<br></li><li> Have you already finished the game once? Try a different way - there are 3 endings and different ways to finish levels.</li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394930/extras/899339daccc9389cb7f3815e9bacde27.poster.avif?t=1716909079\" width=626 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394930/extras/899339daccc9389cb7f3815e9bacde27.webm?t=1716909079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394930/extras/899339daccc9389cb7f3815e9bacde27.mp4?t=1716909079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join our protagonist, Simon - a passenger without a ticket, on an exciting train adventure to get to the capital city. You will have to be smart in order to get a place to sleep during this long trip. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394930/extras/5eae827e1d84664ac74399cb6469fe4d.poster.avif?t=1716909079\" width=626 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394930/extras/5eae827e1d84664ac74399cb6469fe4d.webm?t=1716909079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394930/extras/5eae827e1d84664ac74399cb6469fe4d.mp4?t=1716909079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There are multiple ways to finish almost every level. But you have to speak with passangers carefully and don't forget to use inventory.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394930/extras/1c3b047001fd53a03277363a696b48b5.poster.avif?t=1716909079\" width=626 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394930/extras/1c3b047001fd53a03277363a696b48b5.webm?t=1716909079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2394930/extras/1c3b047001fd53a03277363a696b48b5.mp4?t=1716909079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Choose wisely, your actions influence the final. Help Simon reach the capital in better condition.",
